Package io.github.thebusybiscuit.slimefun4.core.services.plugins

Class ThirdPartyPluginService

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.thebusybiscuit.slimefun4.core.services.plugins.ThirdPartyPluginService

  • public class ThirdPartyPluginService
extends Object
    This Service holds all interactions and hooks with third-party Plugins that are not a dependency or a SlimefunAddon. Integration with these plugins happens inside Slimefun itself.
    Author:
    TheBusyBiscuit
